# Team Flow — Spec

Active commands: `/spec`, `/legacy-spec`, `/bqa-grill-docs`, `/dev-grill-docs`, `/grill-with-docs`, `/update-spec`, `/update-spec-legacy` — one per session.

| Command | Skill |
|---------|-------|
| `/spec` | `.cursor/skills/spec/SKILL.md` |
| `/legacy-spec` | `.cursor/skills/legacy-spec/SKILL.md` |
| `/bqa-grill-docs` | `.cursor/skills/bqa-grill-docs/SKILL.md` |
| `/dev-grill-docs` | `.cursor/skills/dev-grill-docs/SKILL.md` |
| `/grill-with-docs` | `.cursor/skills/grill-with-docs/SKILL.md` |
| `/update-spec` | `.cursor/skills/update-spec/SKILL.md` |
| `/update-spec-legacy` | `.cursor/skills/update-spec-legacy/SKILL.md` |
| Grill metadata rules | `.cursor/rules/team-flow-grill.mdc` |

Shared: resolve skill `extractBundle` → `.cursor/extracts/extract-registry.json` (e.g. `bqa-grill`, `dev-grill`, `grill-with-docs`).

## Pipeline

1. **`/legacy-spec` or `/spec`** — `*.bundle.yaml` design v1 + testcase round 1. No `gen` / `codegen`.
2. **`/bqa-grill-docs`** — UI, acceptance, breadcrumb, delete rules.
3. **`/dev-grill-docs`** — codegen-ready bundle + `tags`; emit FE Codegenkit dry-run handoff.
4. **`/grill-with-docs`** — optional reconcile when BQA↔Dev contradict.
5. **`/update-spec`** / **`/update-spec-legacy`** — controlled delta + `#update:*` (not full rewrite).
6. **`/prototype`** — FE-lane handoff only after Codegenkit dry-run passes.

- Render: `docs_render` / `bundlekit render` (pnpm fallback during transition)
- **Không** prototype UI, backend, real API, full E2E/unit trong phase spec/grill.
